&lt;p&gt;ble_ctf_ A Bluetooth low energy capture the flag :  &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/hackgnar/ble_ctf&#34;&gt;https://github.com/hackgnar/ble_ctf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
